Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:07.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you miraculous illusions \Nthat will make the night sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:11.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I present to you one of my days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Angel's Crown is mine tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:17.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! \NShine it in his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:24.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,C-Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:37.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:39.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! There's a note on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:40.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:44.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"For tonight, I bid you adieu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:47.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,However, I shall return \Nnext Sunday at 8:00 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,to abscond with the Angel's Crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-Make a monkey out of me, will he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, I know that face...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:41.75,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Kaito Kuroba's Busy Day Off
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both of you, stop eating so sullenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The least you could do is tell me\N if the food is any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't any good, it's not like \NI could just come out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:19.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to tell me\N it isn't any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:23.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, your hamburger steaks always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They always crumble into little bitty pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's an awful thing to say! \NAfter I cooked dinner for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell Chikage-san what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Um, do I have something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:41.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaito, you're like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've still got food on your plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll have it for breakfast tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:56.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez. What's he talking about, \N"crumbling into pieces"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:00.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You two are like a married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What makes me seem like\N that jackass's wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you two \Ngo out on dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:14.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What, you're suspicious of us, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So that's why you were \Nstaring at Kaito tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's just silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:34.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure of it. I saw his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:38.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And Kaito-kun performs magic, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All the more suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:48.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief's note claims he'll \Nappear again next Sunday. I'll prove it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way Kaito is \NKid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On what grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, Kaito is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito-kun is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:06.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...going on a date with me next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:17.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you gonna \Nmake me say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go on a date with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is this? Some kind of gag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you accept or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who would go out on a \Ndate with a dog like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:39.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know... I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Really?! Then let's make it next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At Tropical Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,I shall return next Sunday at 8:00 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:05.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sunday's when I'm supposed to appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't believe {\i1}you{\i0} asked {\i1}him{\i0}\N out on a date, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You must really like Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As if I like that jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it because I {\i1}want to{\i0}\N go on a date with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:20.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:24.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is Dad's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:27.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Suspecting Kaito of being \NKid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:30.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not possible... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You were peeping in the girls' locker \Nroom again, weren't you, Kaito-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't use such a cheap lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:47.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not like I was peeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:51.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I heard somebody saw a rat, so I thought \NI'd hunt it down for you, is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}is{\i0} suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The inspector suspects you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:08.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think he saw my face when \NI was on the job last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:12.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He was staring at me all \Nthrough dinner this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And maybe it's not only him, \Nbut Aoko, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko-san too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:23.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, she suddenly insisted \Nthat we go on a date next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next Sunday is when...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:29.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...I said I'd steal the Angel's Crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:34.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. I'd be careful if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:38.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They say there's nothing scarier \Nthan a woman's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty heavy remark \Ncoming from you, Jii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you speaking from experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Young Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:57.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've prepared the props you requested \Nfor your next magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And this, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:12.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,With that, you should be able \Nto make it through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just hope I can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:21.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad, what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kaito,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:36.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As the famous magician Al Baker once said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Don't run away before they chase you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Don't run away before they chase you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:48.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If given a chance, the audience \Nwill begin to doubt us magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:52.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,However, if you fear their gaze, \Nyou'll definitely make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:58.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A first-rate magician never \Nfears being scrutinized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can trust in your own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Loud and clear, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, \NI won't lose my nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:16.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm the son of Toichi Kuroba,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the greatest phantom thief in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:42.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Aoko doesn't suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Don't run away before they chase you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is act normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew you would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I promised, didn't I? Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look! Those elephants are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The elephants are welcoming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's go in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:36.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You people will never leave this room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The painting is stretching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The room is just being lowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Tropical Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You smell sweaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:26.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that's the Aoko I know. \NThis way is more natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! You were just being mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:51.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Dumbass! You gotta eat fish \Nright in front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What can I say? I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:08.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for me \Nto put in an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect chance to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:18.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The movie's 40 minutes. \NAs long as I'm back by the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, 3D movies give me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:29.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:35.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay with me... for just a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's watch the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:42.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Does she know about my other identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:46.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So the inspector {\i1}did{\i0} see my face then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Chill out. Have faith in your own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:08.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now, please enjoy {\i1}Adventures{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:17.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He should be here in ten \Nminutes! Stay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got 34 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:24.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That much time to do the job and get \Nback by Aoko's side! I've gotta make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One more minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know where the inspector went?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! You've got 18 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:07.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You walked right into it, \NKid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:18.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You walked right into my trap! \NAnd now I'll reveal your true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now I'll expose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...your real identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My true identity is... Captain Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:45.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can look like anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:51.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori, I know \N{\i1}everyone{\i0} who's close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then you impersonated \NKaito-kun last time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:16:00.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And I think I'll be {\i1}you{\i0} next time,\N Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:23.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crap! That ate up too much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The movie's gonna be over in nine minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:30.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If I'm not back by then, \NAoko will realize I'm Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:34.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the end of you, Captain Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show you my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,90 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And it's two kilometers away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tropical Land Map
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,3D Movie Adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,You Are Here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Dragon Coaster Waiting Area
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dragon Coaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Turbo Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:48.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:19:06.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Metro police fail to capture \NKid the Phantom Thief again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:59.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, just on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,what can you tell us about tonight's theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:03.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you watching this, \NKid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:06.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll arrest you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, you're just Kaito, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:25.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So to prove my innocence, Aoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,you put me through the wringer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your favorite ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't act out of character!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:46.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if this isn't like me, I'm {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:29.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, Aoko-chan told me what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:33.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was a very cheesy line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:40.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"But ice cream is sweet."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:46.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It wasn't {\i1}that{\i0} bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:52.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've reached the age where \Nyou say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Quit bustin' my chops, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:59.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That reminds me of the first time \Nyour father and I went on a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,More of your nostalgia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It was on the Champs-Élysées in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:08.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your father made reservations \Nat a very fancy restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:14.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mom, sorry to interrupt, but there's \Na show I wanna catch on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Can we wind this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen to me! I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I doubt that very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Talk to you soon. Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:27.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! Everything has to be \Ndone at your pace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who do you get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,From you, Mom, from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So anyway, at that restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the wine was the finest I'd ever tasted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:44.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, let's meet again \Nunder the sweet night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:48.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:24.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For some reason, schools at night \Nhave a really creepy atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But even though everyone's like, \N"There's a ghost!", I don't take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:32.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So this Phantom will get to \Nthe bottom of that ghostie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.50,0:23:35.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's childish to try and \Nexpose a ghost story?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:39.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see for yourself and decide \Nwhether I'm a kid or an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:43.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Adult's Charm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:43.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Adult's Charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:48.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
